column5: Built in 1925, this historic A-frame cabin is the last one of the total of 5 built on our property and the first one restored. These cabins have always been a great historic icon to Lake Cisco. We purchased this property February of 2016 with a goal of restoring the whole facility. Since the purchase, we have made lot of progress and will continue to move forward restoring & modernizing the cabins! Our future plans also include having a store for bait, sporting goods and all your lakeside needs!
